{"tid":2081200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"限制簽證 美懲損港自治京官  參院法案狙擊暴警 惡法推手","createTime":"2020-06-27T04:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T04:57:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"05714917347920a398eab2cab4862e4eb15328ce","tid":2081200,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T04:57:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200627/6LQD2R26CBE3ENLHEY55BHL7NM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2F6LQD2R26CBE3ENLHEY55BHL7NM%2F&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=a16e44d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2F6LQD2R26CBE3ENLHEY55BHL7NM%2F&h=f5d309a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200627/6LQD2R26CBE3ENLHEY55BHL7NM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n限制簽證 美懲損港自治京官 <br />\n參院法案狙擊暴警 惡法推手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國參議院昨一致通過《香港自治法案》，以回應北京強立港版國安法，制裁對象包括實施港區國安法的官員、鎮壓香港示威者的警察及與制裁對象進行生意往來的銀行等。美國國務卿蓬佩奧昨日宣佈，美國會向打擊香港自治、人權和基本自由的中共官員實施簽證限制。民間外交網絡發言人張崑陽認為，首三位料受制裁的官員首推特首林鄭月娥，其次為律政司長鄭若驊和港澳辦主任夏寶龍，張又預料法案很快在眾議院獲通過。眾志黃之鋒指出，制裁最終取決於美國總統特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：白宮一度煞停 與參院磋商釋慮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/siiDa55gxzlBNAD4JgbhbuNePKA=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7Q4EC56VT5XTC7YF7AOCKHC2FM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsiiDa55gxzlBNAD4JgbhbuNePKA%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7Q4EC56VT5XTC7YF7AOCKHC2FM.jpg&h=858b03b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過去一年暴力鎮壓抗爭者的警員料成制裁對象。<br />\n<br />\n繼去年通過《香港人權與民主法案》後，美國參議院以一致同意方式通過《香港自治法案》，提出法案的是民主黨參議員范赫倫（Chris Van Hollen）及共和黨參議員圖米（Pat Toomey）。法案是要回應中共對香港與日俱增的干預，制裁破壞《基本法》和香港自治權的個人或組織，當中包括推動港版國安法的官員、鎮壓香港示威者的警方，以及與制裁對象進行生意來往的銀行等。法案還須在眾議院通過，並由總統特朗普簽署後才會成為法律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n制裁名單最快9月出爐<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧昨表示，曾負責<br />\n...............................<br />\n家屬亦會受牽連。<br />\n<br />\n制裁名單是焦點之一，民<br />\n......................................<br />\n履行《中英聯合聲明》負上責任的非美國籍人士為制裁目標。」<br />\n<br />\n張崑陽其後接受訪問時提到，法案明顯是針對中共強推港版國安法，故硬推法案的官員勢必在名單上。他認為，特首林<br />\n................................................<br />\n眾議院通過，但眾議院長佩洛西十分支持香港，故料可短期內通過。<br />\n<br />\n早前國務卿蓬佩奧稱美國將密切<br />\n...................................<br />\n破壞選舉公平公正的人，或會成為被制裁人士。<br />\n<br />\n大專學界國際事務代表團去年曾製<br />\n.................................<br />\n、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/suxsYuvEYI7IxPK_9sL3Z6zoeSE=/551x689/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KIGNIBLCFUFUR3CMATPNIYXDTE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsuxsYuvEYI7IxPK_9sL3Z6zoeSE%3D%2F551x689%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKIGNIBLCFUFUR3CMATPNIYXDTE.gif&h=8c8d1028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏寶龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0hO6wERR9Mu4cN95__TDkVIp49c=/551x689/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GFQPPHM5I7CQMR4MRKGGEZ37SE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0hO6wERR9Mu4cN95__TDkVIp49c%3D%2F551x689%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGFQPPHM5I7CQMR4MRKGGEZ37SE.gif&h=46911249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2ttnrqKLI-zxsu03CZvFeLSzPhE=/551x689/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B4ZWZM75CVNMETPZI4IQR7VEIQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2ttnrqKLI-zxsu03CZvFeLSzPhE%3D%2F551x689%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB4ZWZM75CVNMETPZI4IQR7VEIQ.gif&h=2b5bceb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭若驊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eEwXqsIDOhXoZ_4ERs6j5e0T4gk=/551x689/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7LGFBJCA2XFMLNDIFAIPTPWFKA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeEwXqsIDOhXoZ_4ERs6j5e0T4gk%3D%2F551x689%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7LGFBJCA2XFMLNDIFAIPTPWFKA.gif&h=664baa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧炳強<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金融機構與被懲者往來勢受罰<br />\n<br />\n法案又授權美國總統透過凍結資產及拒發簽證等措施<br />\n..............................<br />\n控的港人，有資格合法赴美。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒認為，<br />\n.........................<br />\n：「我哋都相信制裁會有唔同討論，但都取決於特朗普。」<br />\n<br />\n特區政府昨晚發稿，對美國參議院通過《香港自治<br />\n.................................<br />\n港的金融機構不具法律效力。我們促請美方以負責任的態度行事，避免採取可能會影響金融機構正常運作及眾多客戶的舉動。」"}]}